Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.58,0:00:39.69,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Love is such a sweet illusion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.79,0:00:41.06,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Let's come together
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:45.35,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Can't seem to stop my imagination
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.45,0:00:46.74,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Goes on forever
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.87,0:00:51.08,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}What a ridiculous situation
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.18,0:00:52.46,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Another matter
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.56,0:00:57.89,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}But I can't deny，I'm faced with a tricky temptation
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.93,0:01:03.30,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}In the world that keeps on changing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.40,0:01:08.56,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Don't know why my heart is aching
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.75,0:01:17.71,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Gotta handle it，no more hesitation
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.90,0:01:20.72,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}There can be no turning back
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.75,0:01:21.88,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}God only knows
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.93,0:01:24.59,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}“My mind is as free as the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.71,0:01:27.96,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}But now what I should do is to fall in love”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.07,0:01:29.14,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}God only knows
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.24,0:01:32.08,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}“I don't need that kind of real things
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.15,0:01:35.41,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Feels like I'm lost in the labyrinth”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.52,0:01:36.58,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}God only knows
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.70,0:01:39.43,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}“There must be the meaning of life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.48,0:01:42.82,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Somehow unexpected happenings thrill me”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.85,0:01:44.00,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}God only knows
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.05,0:01:46.78,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}“Just believe in myself and my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.91,0:01:50.27,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Anyone could be a hero and heroine”
